In current PR, un completed bracket comment won't execute now, for SQL file 
```
/* select /* BROADCAST(b) */ 4;
*/
select  1
;


/* select /* braoad */ ;
select 1;
```

It only execute 
```
/* select /* BROADCAST(b) */ 4;
*/
select  1
;
```

The next part 
```
/* select /* braoad */ ;
select 1;
```
 are still treated as inprogress SQL.
